## ğŸ¯ Hackathon Objective

Collaboratively develop and evaluate a predictive model for your assigned topic, and present your findings to the entire cohort.

Your results will be judged based on:

-   Quality and rigor of your analysis\
-   Clarity and creativity in communicating findings
-   Successful evaluation on an **independent test dataset** where Santa is.

